{"tid":1393800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[芒享]各位打芒享用開咩武器","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T07:59:22.000Z","uid":285367,"like":209,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c85a3430cb7a04044c714248927edb7239d27bc8","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"話說小弟都算元老級玩家 由2G玩到依加<br />\n<br />\n我就從來未見過人打龍 係得個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守</span></span></strong>字既<br />\n我就從來未見過人打龍 係淨用<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">石仔 音爆玉 閃光玉 飛刀</span></span></strong>打得死龍既<br />\n我就從來未見過人打龍 係企係到<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">定點</span></span></strong>同條龍砍既<br />\n我就從來未見過人打龍 係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be water</span></span></strong>Be water跟住<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接退任</span></span></strong>既<br />\n<br />\n講真 打野豬王都算 但係我就打開<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>G位任</strong></span></span> 打開<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">迅龍</span></span></strong> <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">轟龍</span></span></strong> 最近仲岩岩解鎖左新任務<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>水龍三兄弟</strong></span></span> 同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">千里眼龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n依加講緊打龍呀 你估玩泥沙呀 仲得個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>守</strong></span></span>字 你真係想用統槍個盾打贏個任呀<br />\n(sor唔記得左好似無盾擊)<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦 mh打龍嚟講得個防字有咩用呀(唔係話升防無用) 我比全套霸龍裝你又有咩用呀 <br />\n武器得石仔 仲要玩<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全守拋石仔戰術</strong></span></span> 點贏呀 分分鐘條龍都判定太低傷無視你啦<br />\n<br />\n所以 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>防具升級</strong></span></span>係好緊要 但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武器升級</span></strong></span>更為重要 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>心態</strong></span></span>就最為重要<br />\n我見過人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無防裝開火事</strong></span></span>釣起條龍嚟打<br />\n但係無見過人成身霸龍裝但係用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">石頭</span></strong></span>打龍<br />\n<br />\n不過始終我對最新個隻mhxx唔係太熟啦 所以升武器同防具就唔係到多講喇<br />\n聽講屬性武器勁啲<br />\n<br />\n不過心態上反而可以分享下 <br />\n我自己就比較懶 鐘意做啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>必要</strong></span></span>既任務 <br />\n所以攞任前 一定要知道呢個任係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>必須做 </strong></span></span>同埋呢個任<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標</strong></span></span>係咩<br />\n例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打走</strong></span></span>條迅龍啦 定係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打死</strong></span></span>條迅龍 定係打到條迅龍<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">怕</span></strong></span> <br />\n不過呢 就好少有任務係講叫條迅龍回心轉意既<br />\n始終遊戲設計同埋好多朋友實測都係迅龍係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兇殘</span></strong></span>既品種嚟 唔會留手 一野就揮落嚟(條尾)<br />\n<br />\n所以 我比較奇怪既一樣野係 <br />\n點解會有玩家打迅龍個時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只係</strong></span></span>諗點樣擋人地條尾 等條尾打人無咁痛 完全無諗過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>攻</strong></span></span><br />\n直接<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>斷佢尾</strong></span></span>咪出唔到囉?<br />\n迅龍如是 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>水龍</strong></span></span>如是 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>千眼龍</strong></span></span>如是 點解打條龍唔係諗住打<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>部位破壞</strong></span></span> 而係諗住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>單</strong></span></span>靠強化自己防具就可以贏?<br />\n<br />\n另外 都講下一個由初初開始玩芒享會問既問題<br />\n就係點解要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無啦啦</strong></span></span>打啲龍<br />\n咁好簡單姐<br />\n係任務<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>入面</strong></span></span> 你唔解決條迅龍又點樣打下一條<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都係目標</strong></span></span>既龍?<br />\n係任務<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出面</strong></span></span> 你唔解決條迅龍又點繼續下個任 繼續探索呢個芒享既世界?<br />\n<br />\n本身都好少出post 但係好可惜<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好似唔少人都係個任入面迷失左</strong></span></span><br />\n所以麻煩各位 可以好好咁 用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>體技</strong></span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>腦技</strong></span></span>享受芒享 我怕呢個任輸左 就再探索唔到芒享既世界"},{"pid":"71a885722bb51f240d3094d28fa45e080b4c360b","tid":1393800,"uid":40272,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"用開糞彈"},{"pid":"3b7f5412d4e1107650421079006928c70691fe12","tid":1393800,"uid":212927,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"開錯台啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505482c3358d6d1e83b84b5bed634f650c1211c9","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"71a885722bb51f240d3094d28fa45e080b4c360b","tid":1393800,"uid":40272,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"用開糞彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"得 打龍方法有好多種 <br />\n用糞彈姐係想條龍飛去第個區啦<br />\n條龍飛去第個區對你有咩好處 點樣幫你達成到你呢個任務既目標?<br />\n如果只係貪過引 咁就未必係個好戰術了"},{"pid":"74ce2a7ece80720fdaed7aebb1949ea7f1414c85","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"3b7f5412d4e1107650421079006928c70691fe12","tid":1393800,"uid":212927,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:06:36.000Z","msg":"開錯台啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"屌 明明我開遊戲台架 點解會咁"},{"pid":"8707734e6d4f2923e6d27a07d0cc2c0bf0807db3","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"推爆佢 咁既時勢唔打兩鋪機放鬆下點得"},{"pid":"d8c8fa2dd4e675dcc802ac9ef8235a0d268be2c5","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"6148b61f6e7ee0f02016924d63968296fa4c0458","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"再推 唔好只比正評thx"},{"pid":"f21f7cf275309d1b2fa4fb640f97ed6c52fdb866","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:15:44.000Z","msg":"再推 好多人仲傾緊水龍任點拆 緊係係佢訓覺個時打最好"},{"pid":"8ea74967e5724b9374101d3b5a4194e7cd172cee","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d898049e31b7f7ce60823d19d7b913765ba91ea1","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:18:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ae0791fffaa5420537b551004bf2e93fd172f62","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5150a016ed64fa8db2e4c2e04d7530821d272b8","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"推 無人打機?"},{"pid":"935b974a17b4fa32dde6ba81b00f74bc4f4d1192","tid":1393800,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime